snippet.title: Dead Drop - Steam Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Dead Drop on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/587970/

Dead Drop is a tense two-player game of espionage and deception, where one player has to blend into a crowd and mimic AI movement to avoid detection from the other player.

Games reviews and download: http://download.online-games.co/
